init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ask the others why they are all different, but no one has an answer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A few moments later you see your next life play in front of you, and it is that of a white American man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You continue to watch and see that this person is a successful businessman who has a young wife and two children.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You notice that Soeurette's name sounds very familiar, but you brush it off as nothing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You continue watching Matty's life and see how he works hard every day to provide for his family.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You were her lover, back when you lived in an apartment together.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This discovery sends you into a state of shock.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You remember that she was unfaithful and malicious.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You continue to watch Matty's life and see that he eventually finds out that Soeurette is cheating on him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is deeply hurt, and his soul goes through a process known as "soul sickness", where they feel the emotions of their past lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You feel the pain he feels, and you feel the pain of every other person in the cinema.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After Matty realizes that Soeurette has cheated on him, he takes their stepchild and leaves her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are glad that she is being punished for her actions.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The other people in the cinema are also very angry at her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are relieved that she has been punished, and they encourage Matty to continue living his life without her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see Matty move on with his life and you can tell he is extremely happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He meets a woman named Vivian, who is extremely kind.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She realizes her mistakes and regrets everything.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is also jealous of Vivian.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are glad that she is jealous of someone who has earned the love of Matty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matty lives a long and happy life with Vivian.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You spend the rest of your life watching Matty's many happy reincarnations, until your soul is ready to be reborn.
